OL,3,C'It was awful telling my children':
OL,4,CWidow on the toll policing took on
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FA police widow has broken her silence
OL,8,Fto tell UTV about the terrible toll
OL,9,Fthe job took on her husband and why
OL,10,Fshe believes it led to him taking his
OL,11,Fown life.
OL,13,FGary Campbell died by suicide just
OL,14,Fbefore Christmas - less than a year
OL,15,Fafter he retired because of severe
OL,16,Fpost traumatic stress.
