OL,3,C'It was awful telling my children':
OL,4,CWidow on the toll policing took on
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FSusie told UTV "It was awful telling
OL,8,Fmy children. Seeing him in the
OL,9,Fhospital, I will never forget.
OL,10,FAlthough he looked so peaceful. It was
OL,11,Flike all the pain had stopped."
OL,13,F"I will never have peace after this. I
OL,14,Fwill never get over losing him."
OL,16,FJust before he took his own life, Gary
OL,17,Fwrote Susie a letter.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
