OL,3,C'It was awful telling my children':
OL,4,CWidow on the toll policing took on
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,F"He said I was his best friend, I was
OL,8,Fhis world. The last part of the letter
OL,9,Fsaid I wish I never accepted the job
OL,10,Fwith the police, I don't think we
OL,11,Fwould be here now where we are and I
OL,12,Fbelieve that told,'' she said.
OL,14,FGary became a police officer back in
OL,15,F2006 but after almost 20 years
OL,16,Fattending some horrific scenes
OL,17,FSergeant Campbell was emotionally
OL,18,Fshattered.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
