OL,3,C'It was awful telling my children':
OL,4,CWidow on the toll policing took on
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,F"He could see the people's faces in
OL,8,Fdeath, hear their voices, like it was
OL,9,Fhappening all over again."
OL,11,FSusie feels people could have done
OL,12,Fmore to help her husband and claims
OL,13,Fthey didn't even reach out when he was
OL,14,Fbeing treated in hospital for several
OL,15,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
