OL,3,C'It was awful telling my children':
OL,4,CWidow on the toll policing took on
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,F"I grew up with my daddy in the RUC
OL,8,Fand I am very aware of the police
OL,9,Ffamily ethos and values. I feel so let
OL,10,Fdown. Families need their support. I
OL,11,Fneeded them whether it was just to say
OL,12,Fare you ok."
OL,14,FIll-health retirement in the police
OL,15,Fhere is at a record high.
OL,17,FLast week the Chief Constable said he
OL,18,Ftakes the well-being of his officers
OL,19,Fvery seriously.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
