OL,3,C'It was awful telling my children':
OL,4,CWidow on the toll policing took on
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FIn a statement to UTV police said:
OL,8,F"First and foremost our thoughts are
OL,9,Fwith Gary's family following this
OL,10,Ftragic loss.
OL,12,F"As a police service we continually
OL,13,Fwork to protect and support our staff
OL,14,Fto ensure that the risks and pressures
OL,15,Fwhich they can face are minimised.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
