OL,3,C'It was awful telling my children':
OL,4,CWidow on the toll policing took on
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,F"Policing is, by its very nature, a
OL,8,Fhigh risk and challenging profession.
OL,9,FEvery day police officers and staff
OL,10,Fencounter difficult circumstances and
OL,11,Fregrettably, can experience physical
OL,12,Fand/or psychological injury, and the
OL,13,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,14,Ftakes its responsibility to support
OL,15,Fthem very seriously.
OL,17,F"We are committed to continuously
OL,18,Fimproving the range of health and
OL,19,Fwellbeing services and support we
OL,20,Foffer to officers and staff.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
