OL,3,C'It was awful telling my children':
OL,4,CWidow on the toll policing took on
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,F"An independent, fully security-
OL,8,Fvetted, self-referral counselling
OL,9,Fservice is also provided by Lena by
OL,10,FInspire and is available 24 hours a
OL,11,Fday, seven days a week, 365 days a
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,F"We are exploring our wellbeing and
OL,15,Fpreventative capacity to monitor the
OL,16,Fpsychological health of those working
OL,17,Fin higher risk posts so that we can
OL,18,Fprovide early interventions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
