OL,3,C'It was awful telling my children':
OL,4,CWidow on the toll policing took on
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,F"We have created a wellbeing and
OL,8,Ftrauma resilience plan designed to
OL,9,Foffer practical ways to look at mental
OL,10,Fhealth and to safeguard wellbeing. Our
OL,11,Fworkforce can also access a wellbeing
OL,12,Fhub, and are supported by accredited
OL,13,Fvolunteers and post incident peer
OL,14,Fsupport team who work across the
OL,15,Forganisation.
OL,17,F"We recognise the important public
OL,18,Frole that our workforce performs and
OL,19,Fwill continue to invest and support
OL,20,Four people throughout their career in
OL,21,Fpolicing.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
