OL,3,C'It was awful telling my children':
OL,4,CWidow on the toll policing took on
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,F"We further recognise the impact that
OL,8,Fa career in policing can have on
OL,9,Fofficers and staff and we are
OL,10,Fcommitted to ensuring that support
OL,11,Fservices remain available to them upon
OL,12,Fretirement. This includes the Police
OL,13,FRehabilitation and Retraining Trust
OL,14,Fprovision and other foundations that
OL,15,Foffer signposting and support.''
